SIGMA Rule: UAC Bypass Using Registry Shell Open Keys
SIGMA Description: Detects the pattern of UAC Bypass using fodhelper.exe, computerdefaults.exe, slui.exe via registry keys (e.g. UACMe 33 or 62)
